data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value: This project allows the user to enter information about their employees. They can enter the id, name, social security, hourly rate, and hours worked. The program will then calculate the gross pay and net pay and display it into the data grid view. The user can also chose to fire the employee which transfers the information into another table called previous employee. The program also allows the user to search for a current employee and modify their information.
